Special; Getting Out Alive



Aired on 05/09/2014, Narrated by: Stephen Bogaert



This special looked at how flight crew are trained to help people survive aviation accidents, in part with demonstrations at the Czech Airlines Training Centre.

note: I don't know where this is going to fit on a Season Episode basis, there is no word from Cineflix on it's place in the lineup. So for now I've included it as Episode 00 of Season 14 pending clarification.
